<subSubSection id="1C99963913D6F8EA743F409F91013980" pageId="null" pageNumber="58" type="description">
<paragraph id="EFA9728CEE27AF3714F4B09D3531BEFD" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">
Unterscheidet sich von der Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="FB40039FBA8241975AE223251E27489E" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Anemone" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Anemone</taxonomicName>
(S. 47) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="5A41FC3AC7FF1650F6B221A1357C38B7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">
<normalizedToken id="966EE77601CE6AED56CC0192F33DEBDE" originalValue="Hochblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">Hochblaetter</normalizedToken>
ganzrandig, nahe der 
<normalizedToken id="9BF4A54F6F1E7C5ACBF4827D7A9BCFA6" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">Bluete</normalizedToken>
stehend und scheinbar einen Kelch bildend.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B23E9E992EB44D9DF915D7112271FC6E" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">
Die Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="57A0CDA07CE1EE3B5C756B18EA09D4A6" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Hepatica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="28E24332AFD755D67FEFA5E44BB1640B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">Hepatica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="70B261DADB8F66A2C4EB5F4BB7F339B9" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">umfasst</normalizedToken>
etwa 
<emphasis id="9690A380FBC96CB7D031BB66C5A3401F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">6 Arten in Asien und Nordamerika;</emphasis>
in Europa nur 
<taxonomicName id="67B15FD217CC7C5B50D0A79BCBF9A626" authority="Gilib." authorityName="Gilib." class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Hepatica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="triloba">
<emphasis id="1FEAB3FED0ED65CB3CA941B82D724523" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">H. triloba</emphasis>
Gilib.
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="2BB85EC7321C9128A46D0815133F0F5D" authority="Fuss. Chromosomengrundzahl" authorityName="Fuss. Chromosomengrundzahl" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Hepatica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="transsilvanica">
<emphasis id="D7D11DF163DFF981F011D00FBA63FB43" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">H. transsilvanica</emphasis>
Fuss. 
<emphasis id="85EDDC7F1D84AA22AC08264EBCD78F9C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">Chromosomengrundzahl</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ist n = 7. 
<normalizedToken id="89B1CB5A497F95AC0EC2EAA4F24DAD45" originalValue="Über" pageId="null" pageNumber="58">Ueber</normalizedToken>
Zytologie siehe Baumberger (1970).
</paragraph>
